([ "Account":"sendnoodlez", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! EMBROIDERY ! Percival's lustrous gold cashmere tapestry:\<[Ironclaw:Staff:Cersei:Props:Clothing:TapestryBlank]#154315\>, THREAD:Percival's spool of bronze silk thread -\> Covering the entire surface of the tapestry is a monochromatic embroidery of bronze silk thread that portrays an elaborate and lush forest scene. The top half of the piece is a crisscross of branches laden with heavy foliage in a mixture of oak and maple, tiny acorns seen sporadically placed throughout the thick canopy of leaves. Along the foreground, an equally lush ensemble of berry-laden bushes creates a border that encircles the scene displayed at the center of the tapestry. Here, minute stitches create a heavily textured image of two deer frozen in motion. On the right, a doe stands with her head bowed, the expression on her face serene and her eyes half-closed as she grazes peacefully on the acorns that dot the forest floor. Standing opposite, a large buck stands proud, his head held high and the spread of his antlers filling the remainder of the negative space in a mirror of the complex network of branches overhead. Along the lower left-hand corner, a tiny signature in bronze silk thread spells out the word “Whyte” in a minute and spindly script.", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:pe:percival", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Northeast:Tailors:FirstFloor:Back", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Dec 6 09:25): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1607264754", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1607264754", "TimeClosed":"1607264754", "TimeFiled":"1607029846" ])

Polgara's engraved brandywine-stained poplar fireplace:\<[Allegory:Props:Furniture:Fire:Fireplace]#61823\> -\> The surround, framing the fireplace, has been engraved with a series of wintry depictions, which are encased in elongated rope-work frames. \\r\\n\\r\\n Left and right, flanking the hearth's opening, the surround is engraved with coniferous fir trees, whose frost-covered peaks and tips diminish in size and frequency near the top of either columnar side, gradually fading into smatterings of snowflakes, and tufted clouds.\\r\\n\\r\\n The framework just below the mantel has been enclosed by whorls of billowing clouds. A meticulously carved image of a cherub-cheeked old man resides in the left corner, his beard and hair meshing seamlessly with the curls of cloud. Lips pursed, and cheeks puffed out; the man's expelled breath becomes fluid, flowing streaks and swirls of wind, scattering the tiniest of curlicue-borne snowflakes across a topographic map of the Italian peninsula, and its three surrounding seas. The central imagery is capped on either end by nautical starbursts, whose pointed edges have been inscribed with the cardinal directions. ", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:po:polgara", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Northeast:Carpenter:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Dec 6 09:26): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1607264770", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1607264770", "TimeClosed":"1607264770", "TimeFiled":"1607071178" ])

Frederic's box of embossed silver-strewn emerald vellum envelopes:\<[Allegory:Props:Writing:Stationery:BoxEnvelopes]#181703\> -\> Embossed along the border of the envelope is a pastoral winter scene accented by brushstrokes of pure white and golden brown. Snow-laden evergreen trees hug the left and right hand sides of the piece and create a frame for a view of rolling hills and windswept snow banks. A horse-drawn sleigh has been embossed onto one of the most distant hills, the golden brown color in stark contrast to the emerald coloring of the paper. Frederic's box of embossed silver-strewn emerald vellum cards:\<[Allegory:Props:Writing:Stationery:BoxCards]#179950\> -\> The front of the card has been embossed with a lush evergreen tree decorated in hues of red, gold, and silver that complement the silver-flecked emerald of the paper itself. Taller than it is wide, the left-hand side of the card is filled with the image of the tree, small candles highlighted by painted auras of gold to give the impression of light that is carried through in the highlights painted on the red ribbons and silver bows that cover the branches of the tree. Beneath its boughs, a mountain of red painted boxes tied with white string spill over the bottom portion of the card, leaving enough negative space on the right-hand side of the card for a sentiment of holiday greeting. ([ "Account":"lidiab", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! ENGRAVING ! Polgara's engraved quilted silkwood frame loom:\<[Allegory:Props:Tools:Weaver:LoomFrame]#298746\> -\> Along the outer edge of the loom on both the left and right sides, miniature depictions of the process of fabric weaving have been incised.\\r\\n\\r\\n Beginning with a woolly sheep, head bowed as it idly nips at a patch of grass, a pair of fleecy tufts rise aloft from its back end, each narrowing into a spun piece of yarn, which trail to curl around a spindle. ([ "Account":"sendnoodlez", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! EMBROIDERY ! Percival's gold-flecked green cisele velvet tapestry:\<[Ironclaw:Staff:Cersei:Props:Clothing:TapestryBlank]#163374\>, THREAD:Percival's spool of blue silk thread -\> An interpretation of the scene of the Birth of Venus covers the fabric in a myriad of pastel hues that stand in stark contrast to the dark green background of the piece itself. Most prominent at the center of the tapestry is a female figure in the nude, her body stitched in a smooth pattern of cream silk stitches to give the illusion of soft skin as she covers herself with her hands in an attempt to remain modest. She stands upon a seashell that floats atop the water, faint lines of blue stitching giving just an essence of the water before fading into the background. At either side of this figure, two angels in flowing robes hover poised in midair, their wings detailed in cream silk thread to give a realistic feathered texture to each outstretched appendage. The angel on the left wears robes in pale green, the folds billowing in the wind as he reaches outright with splayed fingers. To the right, an angel in pale rose robes holds out a robe in copper color, the hue matching the coruscating waves of Venus' hair that seem to billow behind her in the same ocean breeze that gives dynamic movement to the prolific fabric folds detailed on the tapestry. The remainder of the background is far less detailed in nature, sparse stitching and accents giving the illusion of the horizon, shoreline, and distant trees to the otherwise negative space, allowing the gold-flecked green velvet to remain visible in sumptuous color and texture.", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:pe:percival", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Northeast:Tailors:FirstFloor:Back", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Dec 15 14:20): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1608060000", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1608059999", "TimeClosed":"1608060000", "TimeFiled":"1608059666" ])

PAINTING ! painting of a scroll atop an open book . \\r\\nFilling the canvas is an array of minute, feathery brushstrokes in muted hues of ivory, cream, and burnt umber accented by a splash of pale amethyst seen in a sprig of lavender that is tucked in the pages of an open book. The text of the book is out of focus, allowing the viewer to concentrate on the ornate script that covers the unfurled scroll laying diagonally atop the pages. \\r\\n \\r\\n\\"You have filled a place inside my soul that I didn't know was empty until you fit yourself so perfectly into it.\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\"I will never again know the sorrow of loneliness or the pain of emptiness. I will never again know the incompleteness of life without 'us'. PAINTING ! painting of a white chicken with roses. \\r\\nThe canvas is covered in a large amount of very vibrant paint in haphazard strokes and splotches that appear to have been done by fingers as well as a brush in equal measure. Large white triangle shapes extend from the sides of the round white splotch at the center and two much smaller yellow triangles hover beneath it. ([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a young girl with flowers. \\r\\nThe canvas is covered in a large amount of very vibrant paint in haphazard strokes and splotches that appear to have been done by fingers as well as a brush in equal measure. Prominent in the center of the canvas is a lopsided triangle shape in bright pink paint, the color smudged and muddied in places by swirling blotches of blue. Floating above the point of the triangle is a bright yellow circle that is surrounded entirely by a chaotic swirling circle of brown spirals. Two small brown dots at the top of the circle are roughly centered above a curved pink line that makes for a simple image of a smiling face. Black lines of paint that aren't entirely straight jut out from the sides of the triangle, in addition to two that hover beneath the triangle's base. The tip of the rightmost black line is covered by a large amount of bright pink dots and splotches, the green lines underneath giving the impression that it might be a bouquet of flowers being held aloft by the black stick arm of the figure. Large capital letters that spell out the name \\"SOPHIA\\" can be seen in pink on the bottom of the canvas, the backward S betraying the youth of the artist.\\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#164134\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:to:topsy", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:em:emmaline", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Topsy (Jan 1 01:07): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1609481224", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1609481224", "TimeClosed":"1609481224", "TimeFiled":"1609127708" ])

([ "Account":"ezralee", "Assigned":"", "AssistText":"! PAINTING ! painting of a man with a little girl. \\r\\nThe canvas is covered with a large amount of very vibrant paint in haphazard strokes and splotches that appear to have been done by fingers as well as a brush in equal measure. On the left-hand side of the canvas is a vaguely rectangular shape in dark black and grey colors that have been smudged together in a haphazard fashion that strays occasionally outside the boundary of the shape. Two black lines hover below the shape with another two lines sticking out from either side of the rectangle. A fifth black line extends downward from the leftmost stick arm of the figure to meet with the bright green line that runs horizontally beneath. Above the rectangle is a bright yellow circle, complete with tiny black dot eyes and a curved black line smile, the image finished off by an ovoid black shape hovering just above the yellow circle. Much smaller on the right-hand side of the canvas is a triangular figure in a muddied mixture of pink and black lines, the stick legs hovering beneath the base of the triangle and two stick arms jutting from the sides, the leftmost one connecting to the rightmost arm of the rectangular figure with a bright pink heart shape. The yellow circle smiling face that floats above the top point of the triangle is surrounded by a chaotic swirling circle of brown. Behind the two figures, splotches of bright blue mix with swirls of white in what can only be a representation of the sky. Large capital letters that spell out the name \\"SOPHIA\\" can be seen in pink on the bottom of the canvas, the backward S betraying the youth of the artist.\\r\\n (\<[IronClaw:Props:Artist:Canvas]#163971\>)", "Assistee":"Chatters:AE:kj:kjell", "CharObj":\, "Character":"Chatters:AE:em:emmaline", "Environment":"Allegory:Setting:Rinascita:Buildings:Southeast:PaintShop:Main", "Flag":"", "Links":(\{ \}), "Notes":"\<*\> Kjell (Jan 11 11:35): (discarded)\\n\\n", "Priority":10, "Queue":"custom", "Rev":1.2, "RevTime":"1610382916", "Server":"ironclaw", "Theatre":"IC", "TimeClaimed":"1610382916", "TimeClosed":"1610382916", "TimeFiled":"1609128878" ])
